[src:reasonml/javascript] They shorten the syntax for writing functions in JavaScript.
[src:reasonml/javascript] Arrow functions are anonymous, so a variable is needed to refer to them in order to invoke them after their creation, unless surrounded by parenthesis and executed immediately.
